	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "[Tenth Miracle of Jesus:] (continued) How the soldiers broke the bones of the two thieves; how they came to Jesus and found that he was dead; how one of the commanders saw the miracles and said, “Truly this man is the son of God;” how the arch priest came to Pilate and asked him to burn the body of Jesus; how Pilate refused to burn his body but posted guards at the tomb of Jesus; how Joseph of Arimathea and asked for the body of Jesus; how Joseph and Nicodemus prepared his body and placed it in the tomb; how the Jews gave gold to Pilate to place guards at the tomb. Incomplete at the end" ;
